  "description": "<i>Pirate Pedro</i> is an educational game that teaches basic mathematics for young children. The game can be played with addition, subtraction or a mixture of both and the difficulty level can be set from 1 to 9. Pirate Pedro has lost all his treasure. It has been taken by naughty green spiders and it's up to the player to get the treasure back. To succeed the player has to answer ten maths questions and if more than seven are correct the spiders will give back the treasure to the poor pirate.",
